comments.body:
Moving `RelayAddrsWithConn` to net_processing and making it:

```c++
static inline bool RelayAddrsWithConn(const Node& node, const Peer& peer) {
    return !node.IsBlockOnlyConn() && !peer.m_disable_tx;
}
```

would preserve the net/net_processing separation better, I think?

